{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/story.png?t=1732030677\" />A time travel breakthrough at Waldorp-Verr Aerospace Corporation has come under scrutiny from the US Government. An investigative audit  goes wrong and the research facility is flooded by a prehistoric lake!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as Craig O'Dell, a member of a covert group  tasked with rescuing the only scientist who understands how the time portal works!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/Gameplay.png?t=1732030677\" />Primal Rift is a turn-based, single-character RPG set in a flooded research facility.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Note from the Developer:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">I set out to make a classic solo-character console-style RPG similar to the original Dragon Warrior/Dragon Quest with a few fun twists and no filler. Instead of rescuing a princess in a tower, you will be saving a scientist trapped in a research facility. Instead of swords and magic, you will be using knives and guns. The game also takes place in one large interconnected &quot;dungeon&quot; as opposed to multiple towns and dungeons.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">       <img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/teamArtwork.png?t=1732030677\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/features.png?t=1732030677\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/spiralshell.png?t=1732030677\" /> Meet fascinating prehistoric creatures!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/spiralshell.png?t=1732030677\" /> Make tough life-or-death decisions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/spiralshell.png?t=1732030677\" /> Wield an arsenal of weapons such as knives, SMGs, rifles, and more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/spiralshell.png?t=1732030677\" /> Climb, swim, jump and most importantly fight for your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/spiralshell.png?t=1732030677\" /> Tons of secrets to discover!\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/extras/spiralshell.png?t=1732030677\" /> New Game Plus mode </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732030677","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732030677","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732030677","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405020/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732030677","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":